                </h2>
                <button
                    onClick={() => loadDestinations(true)}
                    disabled={isRefreshing}
                    className="p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/5 text-zinc-500 hover:text-[#10B981] transition-all disabled:opacity-50"
                    title="Refresh Suggestions"
